author: @ioniq5ndriver
text:
To HYBE:

We, the devoted fans of NewJeans, are outraged and deeply disappointed by your recent actions, which we believe are deliberately hindering the progress and success of our beloved girl group. NewJeans has shown immense talent, dedication, and potential, only to be met with unjust treatment that jeopardizes their future.

Your lack of support and questionable decisions have not gone unnoticed. We demand transparency, fairness, and the respect that NewJeans rightfully deserves. It is your responsibility to nurture and promote your artists, not stifle their growth or undermine their efforts.

NewJeans has captured our hearts with their incredible performances and unwavering passion. We want nothing more than to see them continue to thrive and achieve greatness. We believe in their potential to perform brilliantly on the world stage, and we stand ready to support them every step of the way.

This is a call to action: Stand with NewJeans, correct these wrongs, and give them the opportunities they have earned. The fans will not stand idly by while our favorite group is mistreated. We expect better from you, and we will continue to voice our discontent until NewJeans receives the support they need and deserve.

Sincerely,

F•R

author: @킁-w9t
text:
To interpret 'OMG' by Newjeans, one must closely examine the bear in it. The bear is the emblematic animal of Danteworld (Danteworld is known to worship Hwanwoong) During the recording direction for Newjeans, the director gave feedback to Hanni, suggesting that '|' should sound more clearly as 'E' to convey a stronger emphasis As the starting point of the cult conspiracy theory, during a press conference, Min Hee-jin publicly revealed a KakaoTalk message where HYBE allegedly threatened her through the OMG music video. This suspicion arose because the OMG video depicted Danteworld as a mental institution. Additionally, during the press conference, in other scenes where the conversation content was more visible, this KakaoTalk message was pixelated, further fueling suspicions  Despite widespread dissemination across many communities and social media
